data.description: Welcome home to this 2 story home on a finished basement. All new interior paint, new granite countertops and new mini split system in the basement just to name a few. All 4 spacious bedrooms are on the second floor including en suite primary bedroom/bathroom and 3 other bedrooms with bathroom in hall. Stainless steel appliances in the kitchen make this a bakers dream and open to family room with fireplace. There is a deck off the family room overlooking backyard. Separate dining and living room . Come check it out today!!
